{
  "stem": "1677.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were destitute solicitors shoveling snow, because they were not prepared for not being a solicitor from one day to the other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were struck off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Doctors struck off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Children out of school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, if you follow the Holocaust procedure, this was the expulsion of the economy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you start with education-- you give them away the education, take away their lawyers, take away their solicitors, and our people will become smart.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they explained me-- I did not understand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were standing there, 1st of September, assembly, waiting to go to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My handbag, my school bag-- comes Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Pollack, I so remember, a Czech-- that was bad news in Slovakia in these days, as bad as Jewish-- with a limp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody limped in my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he comes there, and says, would please the following students step out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he reads, Buhola, Brill, Haas, Weiss, Weiss-- they were twins-- so six of us stepped out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, in the name of the republic, you are expelled from state public education forever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My world-- I thought, I don't hear proper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, Kitty Haas, expelled from education?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He should be honored that I come to his stupid school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So came the janitor with a-- with a box of old newspaper-- and limped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was also one of these war-damaged people-- and he laughed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He laughed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went to him, skipped the assembly, walked towards him and said, 'Why are you laughing?' He said, 'At you, because now you are going to be stupid, and we are going to be smart.'",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I looked at him, I was 11 years old, I swore to myself that no one ever is going to call me stupid, ever, ever again.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this will all come into my book.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
